arStrings.szText:
Gain {c_number}[100-Affix_Value_1|%|]{/c} Resource Cost Reduction.

Each time you spend Primary Resource on a Skill, you gain {c_random}[Affix_Value_2|%x|]{/c} increased damage but {c_number}[Affix_Value_1|%+|]{/c} increased Resource costs for {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} seconds, stacking up to {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 1"]{/c} times.
